channels.title: Cocomelon - Nursery Rhymes
channels.description:
At CoComelon, our primary goal has always been to engage families with entertaining and educational content that makes universally-relatable preschool moments fun. 
Our beautiful 3D animation and toe-tapping songs create a world that centers on the everyday experiences of young children. 
In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, 
the videos impart prosocial life lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children as they watch together.

CoComelon. Where kids can be happy and smart!

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon - It's Cody Time
Related_Channel.description:
Join Cody Green - the little kid with a big imagination and an even bigger heart - in this spinoff series set in the familiar, beloved community of CoComelon!

Cody is now a big brother and he's ready to share all-new adventures full of music, games, creativity, and dinosaurs! Whether it’s going to nursery or playing at home, there is always something new for Cody to learn or explore, and endless inspiration for your child!

In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, It's Cody Time imparts key social lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children.

SUBSCRIBE NOW to catch new episodes every Wednesday!

Website ► https://cocomelon.com/ 
Facebook ►https://www.facebook.com/CoComelonKids 
Instagram ►https://www.instagram.com/cocomelon_official/ 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@cocomelon_moonbug?lang=en 
US Shop ► https://shop.moonbug.com/collections/cocomelon

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon en Español - Canciones Infantiles
Related_Channel.description:
En CoComelon, nuestro objetivo es entretender a toda la familia con contenido divertido y educativo, haciendo más divertida esa etapa preescolar de los niños. Nuestras animaciones y canciones llenas de energía crean un mundo dedicado a las experiencias cotidianas de los niños pequeños. Además de ayudar a los niños en esa edad a aprender letras, números, colores y más, los vídeos imparten lecciones de vida prosocial, brindando a los padres la oportunidad de enseñar y jugar con sus hijos mientras vean los vídeos.

¡Este es el lugar donde los niños pueden ser felices e inteligentes!

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon em Português - Músicas Infantis
Related_Channel.description:
Bem vindo ao canal português da série animada CoComelon! Subscreva ao nosso canal para desenhos animados e músicas infantis dublados em português, quatro vezes por semana!

No CoComelon, o nosso principal objetivo sempre foi envolver as famílias com conteúdo divertido e educacional que tornasse os momentos da pré-escola divertidos.

As nossas músicas e animações 3D criam um mundo centrado nas experiências cotidianas de crianças pequenas.
Além de ajudar crianças em idade pré-escolar a aprender letras, números, sons de animais, cores e muito mais,
os vídeos transmitem lições de vida pró-social, proporcionando aos pais a oportunidade de ensinar e brincar com seus filhos enquanto assistem juntos!

Redes Sociais:
🍉Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/4Clpd9b9gDyaYoTfdxyAzJ?si=aVlKKZCERbeX8HI4-SHJiQ
🍉Website: http://www.CoComelon.com 
🍉Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CoComelonkids 
🍉Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/CoComelonkids

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon Deutsch - Kinderlieder
Related_Channel.description:
Wo Kinder glücklich und klug sein dürfen!

CoComelon ist eine unterhaltsame und lehrreiche Show für Kinder mit klassischen und neuen Kinderliedern, die von Kleinkindern und ihren Eltern auf der ganzen Welt geliebt werden. Die 3D-Animationen und Songs von CoComelon schaffen eine Welt, in der die alltäglichen Erfahrungen kleiner Kinder im Mittelpunkt steht.
Die Videos helfen Vorschulkindern nicht nur dabei, Buchstaben, Zahlen, Tierstimmen, Farben und anderes zu lernen, sondern vermitteln Verhaltensregeln und bieten Eltern die Möglichkeit, gemeinsam mit ihren Kindern zu spielen.

Related_Channel.title: Cocomelon Arabic - كوكوميلون أغاني للأطفال
Related_Channel.description:
في كوكو ميلون ، كان هدفنا الأساسي دائمًا إشراك العائلات بمحتوى ترفيهي وتعليمي يجعل لحظات ما قبل المدرسة ممتعة.
تخلق الرسوم المتحركة ثلاثية الأبعاد الجميلة وأغاني الأطفال التعليمية عالماً يركز على التجارب اليومية للأطفال الصغار.
بالإضافة إلى مساعدة الأطفال في مرحلة ما قبل المدرسة على تعلم الحروف والأرقام وأصوات الحيوانات والألوان والمزيد ،
تنقل مقاطع الفيديو دروسًا في الحياة الاجتماعية ، مما يوفر للآباء فرصة للتدريس واللعب مع أطفالهم أثناء مشاهدتهم معًا.

كوكو ميلون. حيث يمكن للأطفال أن يكونوا سعداء وأذكياء!

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon Italiano - Canzoni per Bambini
Related_Channel.description:
CoComelon, Dove i bambini possono essere felici e intelligenti!

CoComelon è un canale divertente ed educativo per bambini con filastrocche classiche amate dai bambini piccoli e dai loro genitori in tutto il mondo. Le animazioni e le canzoni 3D di CoComelon creano un mondo che si concentra sulle esperienze quotidiane dei bambini piccoli.
I video, non solo aiutano i bambini in età prescolare a imparare le lettere, i numeri, i versi di animali, i colori ed altre cose, ma insegnano anche le regole di comportamento e offrono ai genitori l'opportunità di giocare con i propri figli.

Iscriviti per nuovi cartoni animati e canzoni per bambini ogni settimana con CoComelon!!! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCx1j2WcHMRotdFvBBSr8hAg?sub_confirmation=1

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon на русском — Детские песенки
Related_Channel.description:
В мультфильме CoComelon Джей-Джей с братом и сестрой отправляются в увлекательные приключения. Независимо от того, где происходит действие, в детском саду или дома, всегда найдется что-то новое для изучения и исследования, а также бесконечное вдохновение для игр с друзьями и семьей.

Помимо помощи дошкольникам в изучении букв, цифр, звуков животных, цветов и многого другого,
видеоролики передают ключевые социальные уроки, предоставляя родителям возможность обучать и играть со своими детьми во время совместного просмотра.

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon Bahasa Indonesia - Lagu Anak Anak
Related_Channel.description:
Di CoComelon, JJ dan saudara-saudaranya melakukan petualangan yang menyenangkan – baik dengan mengunjungi kamar anak-anak atau tinggal di rumah, selalu ada sesuatu yang baru yang dapat dipelajari atau dijelajahi, dan yang memberikan inspirasi tiada akhir dalam memanfaatkan waktu bermain dengan teman dan keluarga.

Selain membantu anak-anak prasekolah belajar huruf, angka, suara binatang, warna, dan banyak lagi,
video ini memberikan pelajaran sosial utama, membuat orang tua memiliki kesempatan untuk mengajar dan bermain dengan anak-anak mereka saat mereka menonton bersama.

Related_Channel.description:
कोकोमेलन में, जेजे और उसके भाई-बहन मजेदार रोमांचक रोमांच पर जाते हैं - चाहे वह नर्सरी में जाना हो या घर पर रहना, सीखने या तलाशने के लिए हमेशा कुछ नया होता है, और दोस्तों और परिवार के साथ खेलने के समय का अधिकतम लाभ उठाने के लिए अंतहीन प्रेरणा होती है।

प्री स्कूल के बच्चों को अक्षरों, संख्याओं, जानवरों की आवाज, रंग और बहुत कुछ सीखने में मदद करने के अलावा,
वीडियो प्रमुख सामाजिक सबक प्रदान करते हैं, माता-पिता को अपने बच्चों को एक साथ देखने और उनके साथ खेलने का अवसर प्रदान करते हैं।

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon Tamil - குழந்தை பாடல்கள்
Related_Channel.description:
கோகோமிலானில், ஜேஜேவும் அவரது உடன்பிறந்தவர்களும் வேடிக்கைசார்ந்த சாகசங்கள் புரிகிறார்கள் -- அது நர்சரிக்கு செல்வதாக இருந்தாலும், வீட்டில் தங்கியிருப்பதாக இருந்தாலும், கற்றுக்கொள்வதற்கும், ஆராய்வதற்கும் ஏதாவது புதிய விஷயம் எப்போதும் இருக்கும் மற்றும் நண்பர்கள் மற்றும் குடும்பத்தினருடன் விளையாடும் நேரத்தை அதிகம் பயன்படுத்துவதற்கான முடிவற்ற உத்வேகமும் இருக்கும்.

எழுத்துக்கள், எண்கள், விலங்கு சத்தங்கள், வண்ணங்கள் மற்றும் பலவற்றைக் கற்றுக்கொள்வதற்கு பாலர் குழந்தைகளுக்கு உதவுவதோடு, பெற்றோர்கள் அவர்களது குழந்தைகளுடன் சேர்ந்து இந்த காணொளிகளை பார்க்கும்போது, அவர்களது குழந்தைகளுடன் விளையாடுவதற்கும், அவர்களுக்கு கற்பிப்பதற்குமான முக்கிய சமூக பாடங்களை இந்த காணொளிகள் வழங்குகின்றன.

புதிப்பிப்புகளுக்கு பின்பற்றவும் இன்ஸ்டாகிராம் @moonbugentertainment மற்றும் ஃபேஸ்புக் @MoonbugEntertainment!

Related_Channel.title: โคโค่เมล่อน ภาษาไทย - เพลงเด็ก
Related_Channel.description:
"ในโคโค่เมล่อน เจเจและพี่น้องของเขาได้เดินทางไปในการผจญภัยที่สนุกสนาน ไม่ว่าจะเป็นสถานรับเลี้ยงเด็กหรือที่บ้าน มีสิ่งใหม่ๆ ให้เรียนรู้หรือสำรวจอยู่เสมอ และรับแรงบันดาลใจไม่รู้จบในการใช้เวลาเล่นกับเพื่อนๆ และครอบครัวๆ ให้เต็มที่

นอกจากจะช่วยเด็กก่อนวัยเรียนให้เรียนรู้ตัวอักษร ตัวเลข เสียงของสัตว์ สี และสิ่งอื่นๆ แล้ว 
วิดีโอเหล่านี้ยังให้บทเรียนทางสังคมที่สำคัญ โดยให้โอกาสผู้ปกครองในการสอนและเล่นกับลูกๆ ของพวกเขาในขณะที่รับชมด้วยกัน

ติดตาม @moonbugentertainment ทาง IG และติดตาม @MoonbugEntertainment ทาง FB เพื่อรับข่าวสารอัปเดต!

TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@cocomelon_moonbug?lang=en 
ร้านค้าในสหรัฐ ► https://shop.moonbug.com/collections/cocomelon"

코코멜론의 3D 애니메이션과 동요들은 어린아이들의 일상적인 경험에 초점을 맞춘 세상을 만듭니다. 그곳은 아이들이 행복하고 현명해질 수 있는 곳이에요! 코코멜론의 동영상들은 미취학 아동들이 글자, 숫자, 동물 소리, 색깔 등을 배우도록 도울 뿐만 아니라, 친사회적인 삶의 교훈을 전달하여 부모들이 자녀들과 함께 시청하면서 가르치고 놀 수 있는 기회를 제공합니다.

Related_Channel.description:
ココメロンでは、JJと彼のきょうだいたちが楽しく共感できる冒険に出かけます。保育園に行くときも、家にいるときも、常に何か新しいことを学んだり、探検したりと、友だちや家族と一緒に遊ぶ時間を最大限に活用して無限の想像力が身に着けられるようになります。

就学前のお子様が文字や数字、動物の鳴き声、色などを学べるだけでなく、この動画では保護者の方も一緒に見ながら、教えたり、遊んだりしながらお子様に社会性を身につけさせることができる内容です。

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon - Bebek Şarkıları
Related_Channel.description:
CoComelon’da JJ ve kardeşleri her bölüm eğlenceli maceralara atılır. CoComelon bölümlerinde ister kreşte olsunlar ister evde, her zaman öğrenecek ve keşfedecek yeni şeyler, arkadaşlarınızla ve ailenizle geçirdiğiniz zamana değer katacak sonsuz ilham vardır. 

CoComelon'da izleyeceğiniz videolar, okul öncesi dönemdeki çocukların harfleri, sayıları, hayvanları, renkleri öğrenmesinin yanı sıra sosyal becerilerinin gelişmesine de yardımcı olacaktır. Ayrıca CoComelon videoları, ebeveynlerin de çocuklarıyla birlikte izleyebileceği, izlerken çocuklarını eğitmelerine yardımcı olabilecek ve birlikte yeni oyunlar geliştirmelerini sağlayacak niteliktedir. 

Güncellemelerden haberdar olmak için Instagram’da @moonbugentertainment ve Facebook’ta  @MoonbugEntertainment hesaplarını TAKİP EDİN!

"Trong CoComelon, JJ và các anh chị em của mình tham gia vào những cuộc phiêu lưu thú vị có liên quan - cho dù đó là đi nhà trẻ hay ở nhà, luôn có điều gì đó mới để học hỏi hoặc khám phá và nguồn cảm hứng bất tận để tận dụng tối đa thời gian vui chơi với bạn bè và gia đình.

Ngoài việc giúp trẻ mẫu giáo học bảng chữ cái, con số, âm thanh động vật, màu sắc và hơn thế nữa,
các video truyền đạt các bài học xã hội quan trọng, cung cấp cho cha mẹ cơ hội để dạy và chơi với con khi xem cùng trẻ.

THEO DÕI @moonbugentertainment trên IG và @MoonbugEntertainment trên FB để cập nhật thông tin!

Website ► https://cocomelon.com/ 
Facebook ►https://www.facebook.com/CoComelonKids 
Instagram ►https://www.instagram.com/cocomelon_official/ 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@cocomelon_moonbug?lang=en 
Cửa hàng tại Mỹ ► https://shop.moonbug.com/collections/cocomelon"

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon Nederlands - Kinderliedjes
Related_Channel.description:
In CoComelon beleven JJ en zijn broers en zussen leuke, herkenbare avonturen. Of ze nu naar de kleuterschool gaan of thuis blijven, er is altijd wel iets nieuws te leren of te verkennen en er is eindeloze inspiratie om alles uit de tijd met je vrienden en je gezin te halen.

De video's helpen kleuters met het leren van letters, cijfers, dierengeluiden, kleuren en meer. Daarnaast helpen ze met belangrijke sociale lessen en geven ze ouders de kans om samen met hun kinderen te spelen en te leren.

VOLG @moonbugentertainment op IG en @MoonbugEntertainment op FB voor updates!

Related_Channel.title: ¡CoComelon! - Juega y Baila en Español Latino
Related_Channel.description:
¡Juega y Baila con CoComelon en Español Latino!

En CoComelon, nuestro objetivo es entretender a toda la familia con contenido divertido y educativo, haciendo más divertida esa etapa preescolar de los niños. Nuestras animaciones y canciones llenas de energía crean un mundo dedicado a las experiencias cotidianas de los niños pequeños. Además de ayudar a los niños en esa edad a aprender letras, números, colores y más, los vídeos imparten lecciones de vida prosocial, brindando a los padres la oportunidad de enseñar y jugar con sus hijos mientras vean los vídeos.

¡Este es el lugar donde los niños pueden ser felices e inteligentes!

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon Svenska - Barnvisor
Related_Channel.description:
I CoComelon ger sig JJ och hans syskon ut på roliga och lättförståeliga äventyr – oavsett om de går på förskolan eller stannar hemma finns det alltid något nytt att lära sig eller utforska, och oändlig inspiration för att få ut det mesta av lektiden med vänner och familj.

Förutom att hjälpa förskolebarn att lära sig bokstäver, siffror, djurläten, färger och mycket mer ger filmerna viktiga sociala lärdomar och ger föräldrarna möjlighet att undervisa och leka med sina barn när de tittar tillsammans.

FÖLJ @moonbugentertainment på IG och @MoonbugEntertainment på FB för uppdateringar!

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon Dansk - Børnerim
Related_Channel.description:
I CoComelon tager JJ og hans søskende på sjove eventyr, du kan relatere til - uanset om det er at gå i vuggestue eller blive hjemme, er der altid noget nyt at lære eller udforske og uendelig inspiration til at få mest muligt ud af legetid med venner og familie.

Ud over at hjælpe børn i daginstitutioner med at lære bogstaver, tal, dyrelyde, farver m.m. giver videoerne vigtige sociale lektioner, der giver forældre mulighed for at undervise og lege med deres børn, mens de ser dem sammen.

FØLG @moonbugentertainment på IG og @MoonbugEntertainment på FB for opdateringer!

Hjemmeside ► https://cocomelon.com/ 
Facebook ►https://www.facebook.com/CoComelonKids 
Instagram ►https://www.instagram.com/cocomelon_official/ 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@cocomelon_moonbug?lang=en 
US Shop ► https://shop.moonbug.com/collections/cocomelon

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon Suomeksi – Lastenlaulut
Related_Channel.description:
CoComelonissa JJ ja hänen sisaruksensa aloittavat mukaansatempaavan seikkailun – olipa kyseessä lastentarhaan meno tai kotona oleskelu, aina on jotain uutta opittavaa ja tutkittavaa ja loppumatonta inspiraatiota, joiden avulla saat kaiken irti leikkihetkestä ystävien ja perheen kanssa.

Sen lisäksi, että se auttaa esikoululaisia oppimaan kirjaimia, numeroita, eläinten ääniä, värejä ja muuta, videot opettavat keskeisiä sosiaalisia taitoja ja antavat vanhemmille mahdollisuuden opettaa ja leikkiä lastensa kanssa.

SEURAA @moonbugentertainment Instagramissa ja @MoonbugEntertainment Facebookissa saadaksesi päivityksiä!

Related_Channel.title: CoComelon Norsk - Barnerim
Related_Channel.description:
I CoComelon drar JJ og søsknene hans på morsomme, relatable eventyr - enten det er barnehage eller hjemme, det er alltid noe nytt å lære eller utforske, og uendelig inspirasjon for å få mest mulig ut av leketid med venner og familie.

I tillegg til å hjelpe førskolebarn med å lære bokstaver, tall, dyrelyder, farger og mer,
videoene gir viktige sosiale leksjoner, og gir foreldre mulighet til å undervise og leke med barna sine mens de ser sammen.

FØLG @moonbugentertainment på IG og @MoonbugEntertainment på FB for oppdateringer!

Related_Channel.title: Little Baby Bum - Nursery Rhymes & Kids Songs
Related_Channel.description:
Little Baby Bum follows the musical adventures of Mia, Twinkle the Star and Baby Max. Everyday moments like bath time, getting dressed, or playing peekaboo become even more fun with new and classic nursery rhymes.

Little Baby Bum is an animated musical show that celebrates early childhood experiences and supports cognitive development through loveable characters, relatable stories and the magic of song, repetition, rhythm, and rhyme.

FOLLOW
IG @moonbugentertainment : https://www.instagram.com/moonbugentertainment/
FB @MoonbugEntertainment : https://www.facebook.com/MoonbugEntertainment   

Moonbug Entertainment is behind some of the most popular kids’ titles in the world. Moonbug's shows include global sensations CoComelon, Blippi, Little Baby Bum, My Magic Pet Morphle, Supa Strikas, Go Buster, Playtime with Twinkle, Gecko’s Garage, ARPO and many more. Moonbug's titles are available in 27 languages on all major streaming platforms.

Related_Channel.title: Singalong with Cody! - CoComelon
Related_Channel.description:
Join Cody Green - the little kid with a big imagination and an even bigger heart - in this spinoff series set in the familiar, beloved community of CoComelon!

Cody is now a big brother and he's ready to share all-new adventures full of music, games, creativity, and dinosaurs! Whether it’s going to nursery or playing at home, there is always something new for Cody to learn or explore, and endless inspiration for your child!

In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, It's Cody Time imparts key social lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children.

SUBSCRIBE NOW to catch new episodes every Wednesday!

Related_Channel.title: Cody and JJ - CoComelon Nursery Rhymes
Related_Channel.description:
Join Cody Green - the little kid with a big imagination and an even bigger heart - in this spinoff series set in the familiar, beloved community of CoComelon!

Cody is now a big brother and he's ready to share all-new adventures full of music, games, creativity, and dinosaurs! Whether it’s going to nursery or playing at home, there is always something new for Cody to learn or explore, and endless inspiration for your child!

In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, It's Cody Time imparts key social lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children.

SUBSCRIBE NOW to catch new episodes every Wednesday!

Facebook ►https://www.facebook.com/CoComelonKids

Related_Channel.title: Cody and Friends - CoComelon
Related_Channel.description:
Join Cody Green - the little kid with a big imagination and an even bigger heart - in this spinoff series set in the familiar, beloved community of CoComelon!

Cody is now a big brother and he's ready to share all-new adventures full of music, games, creativity, and dinosaurs! Whether it’s going to nursery or playing at home, there is always something new for Cody to learn or explore, and endless inspiration for your child!

In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, It's Cody Time imparts key social lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children.

SUBSCRIBE NOW to catch new episodes every Wednesday!

Related_Channel.title: Cody's Playtime - CoComelon Nursery Rhymes
Related_Channel.description:
Join Cody Green - the little kid with a big imagination and an even bigger heart - in this spinoff series set in the familiar, beloved community of CoComelon!

Cody is now a big brother and he's ready to share all-new adventures full of music, games, creativity, and dinosaurs! Whether it’s going to nursery or playing at home, there is always something new for Cody to learn or explore, and endless inspiration for your child!

In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, It's Cody Time imparts key social lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children.

SUBSCRIBE NOW to catch new episodes every Wednesday!

Website ► https://cocomelon.com/ 
Facebook ►https://www.facebook.com/CoComelonKids 
Instagram ►https://www.instagram.com/cocomelon_official/

About It's Cody Time:
CoComelon just got a whole lot Greener. Join Cody Green - the little kid with a big imagination and an even bigger heart - in this spinoff series set in the familiar, beloved community of CoComelon!

About CoComelon: 
CoComelon’s 3D animation and songs create a world that centers on the everyday experiences of young children. It is a place where kids can be happy and smart! In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, the videos impart prosocial life lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children as they watch together.

PlaylistItems.title: The Three Little Friends Song | CoComelon Animal Time | Animals for Kids
PlaylistItems.description:
Oh no! Wally be careful with your saxophone! JJ, Benny, and Kiki (the three little friends) each construct houses out of straw, sticks, and bricks. But when Wally struts through town, passionately blowing into his saxophone. But, when botching his notes, the force is so powerful he accidentally blows his neighbor’s houses down! If you like the Three Little Pigs, you'll love the Three Little Friends! 
Subscribe for new videos every week: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfXdCQfn2Wly74kX-vyPubw?sub_confirmation=1
Lyrics: 
VERSE 1
Three little friends went out one day
One built a house made out of hay
The other friends thought it would fall, fall, fall
But the first didn’t care at all.
VERSE 2
Three little friends went out one day
The second used sticks to build away
The third friend thought it would fall, fall, fall
But the second didn’t care at all.
VERSE 3
Three little friends went out one day
For the third friend, bricks were the way
He knew the house wouldn’t fall, fall, fall
So the work didn’t bother him at all.
VERSE 4
Then came a wolf who was big and proud
He’d play his sax incredibly loud
The three little friends heard the wolf that day
They slammed their doors and hid away
VERSE 5
“Little friend, little friend, play with me!”
But he’s so noisy, they couldn’t hear a thing
Then he played his wild saxophone so loud!
Short Musical interlude- ending with botched note
And boy, did the hay house go!
VERSE 6
“Little friend, little friend, play with me!”
But he’s so noisy, they couldn’t hear a thing
Then he played his wild saxophone so loud!
Short Musical interlude- ending with botched note
And boy, did the stick house go!

VERSE 7
“Little friend, little friend, play with me!”
But he’s so noisy, they couldn’t hear a thing
Then he played his wild saxophone so loud!
Short Musical interlude- ending with botched note
But the bricks surely did not go!

VERSE 8
The two little friends of hay and sticks
Learned a lesson all about work and bricks
A hard-worked job won’t fall fall fall
To a huff, or a puff, at all!

JJ’s best animal pals are back and sillier than ever! Sing along with JJ and his friends on their wild and hilarious adventures featuring fairy tales, fables, nursery rhymes, and so much more. 

At CoComelon, our primary goal has always been to engage families with entertaining and educational content that makes universally-relatable preschool moments fun. Our beautiful 3D animation and toe-tapping songs create a world that centers on the everyday experiences of young children. In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, the videos impart prosocial life lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children as they watch together.

About It's Cody Time:
CoComelon just got a whole lot Greener. Join Cody Green - the little kid with a big imagination and an even bigger heart - in this spinoff series set in the familiar, beloved community of CoComelon!

About CoComelon: 
CoComelon’s 3D animation and songs create a world that centers on the everyday experiences of young children. It is a place where kids can be happy and smart! In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, the videos impart prosocial life lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children as they watch together.

About It's Cody Time:
CoComelon just got a whole lot Greener. Join Cody Green - the little kid with a big imagination and an even bigger heart - in this spinoff series set in the familiar, beloved community of CoComelon!

About CoComelon: 
CoComelon’s 3D animation and songs create a world that centers on the everyday experiences of young children. It is a place where kids can be happy and smart! In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, the videos impart prosocial life lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children as they watch together.

PlaylistItems.title: Magical Mirror Mila - Cartoons & Stories for Kids
PlaylistItems.description:
Enjoy this special My Magic Pet Morphle adventure, 'Magical Mirror Mila'. As Mila, Morphle and Chroma leave the Magic Pet Center, Mirror Mila escapes from the mirror world. Mila and Morphle have to find a way to return Mirror Mila to the Mirrorworld!

🔴 Subscribe to Morphle TV Here: https://www.youtube.com/user/MagicPetsSongs4Kids?sub_confirmation=1

Welcome to Mila's Magic world! Mila’s dad runs the only magic pet store in the city - a fantastical place where you can find all sorts of cute and quirky pets who each have their own unique magic powers, and he has gifted Mila the most magic pet of all, Morphle. Morphle is an energetic little red creature who can morph into anything: a sweet puppy, a giant truck, a cool dinosaur or anything that Mila’s playful mind can imagine.

🔴 Check out NEWEST Morphle and Mila episodes here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=epyIoBsRFUQ&list=PLmwpvieHKxgFq02SdiE9QlKexrSZYQajA&index=1

PlaylistItems.title: CoComelon - MyGo! Sign Language for Kids
PlaylistItems.description:
We believe all kids should have access to good quality entertainment - regardless of geography, culture, background or abilities. This is why we are making our hugely popular kids show 'CoComelon' available to all kids in ASL.

At CoComelon, our primary goal has always been to engage families with entertaining and educational content that makes universally-relatable preschool moments fun. 

Our beautiful 3D animation and toe-tapping songs create a world that centers on the everyday experiences of young children. 

In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, 
the videos impart prosocial life lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children as they watch together.

We believe all kids should have access to good quality entertainment - regardless of geography, culture, background or abilities. This is why we are making our hugely popular kids show 'CoComelon' available to all kids in ASL.

Having a common cultural frame of reference is incredibly important for kids. And we are acutely aware that there is not currently the same abundance of content and choice available to kids who are deaf and hard-of-hearing, which other kids have. Which is why we are now signing our new content so that every kid, regardless of their abilities, can also enjoy and learn with CoComelon.
